TITLE.P: The Establishment of Multi Party Framework Agreements for Works Projects in Residential, Non-Residential & Heritage. Each Framework from 1-4 will have 5 Lots.

SHORT_DESCR.P: The Establishment of Multi Party Framework Agreements for Residential, Non-Residential and Heritage Works Projects over 4 Frameworks in 5 geographical Lots outline herewith:
— Lot 1: Dublin City Council,
— Lot 2: Fingal County Council,
— Lot 3: South Dublin County Council,
— Lot 4: Dun Laoghaire-Rathdown County Council and.
— Lot 5: Wicklow County Council.
This Framework also includes an option for Local Authorities to appoint Agents of Current and Future Members for the Irish Council of Social Housing.
Multi Party Framework Agreements for Works.
Projects with a value of less than €1,000,000.
FRAMEWORK 1: Lot 1 - Dublin City Council.
This Framework also includes an option for Local.
Authorities to appoint Agents of Current and Future.
Members for the Irish Council of Social Housing.

RENEWAL_DESCR.P: 24 month Framework Agreement with the option to extend the Agreement for a further 24 month period.
